<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Quercus coccifera" order="Fagales" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="coccifera">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Quercus coccifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., 
<taxonomicName class="Pinopsida" family="Cupressaceae" genus="Juniperus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Juniperus oxycedrus" order="Pinales" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Coniferophyta" rank="species" species="oxycedrus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Juniperus oxycedrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Anacardiaceae" genus="Pistacia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pistacia terrebinthus" order="Sapindales" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="terrebinthus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Pistacia terrebinthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
M.Bieb. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">etc.)</emphasis>
. Plant diversity in this place is mainly composed of herbaceous and suffruticose plants including 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Adonis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Adonis flammea" order="Ranunculales" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="flammea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Adonis flammea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Jacq., 
<taxonomicName class="Monocotyledoneae" family="Poaceae" genus="Aegilops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Aegilops cylindrica" order="Graminales" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="cylindrica">
